        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4481",
        "content": "\"Sir,\" said he, sternly-he always called his brother in law \"sir\" when he was in a sarcastic or reproachful mood-\"I've had an idea for some time that you were plotting mischief.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
