        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4481",
        "content": "His affection for the little man increased mightily, but his respectful attitude promptly changed, and a chance to reprove or discomfit his absurdly rich brother in law was one of his most satisfactory diversions.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
