        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4481",
        "content": "The \"we\" is explained by stating that the Major held an important position in the great banking house-a position mr Merrick had secured for him some months previously.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
